# Copy to `.env` or `.env.local` next to `package.json`. Restart `npm run dev` after changes.
# Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to the browser.

# Optional — backend origin (scheme + host + port, no trailing slash).
# Leave unset to use relative URLs (`/api/...`): in dev, Vite proxies `/api` to the target in `vite.config.ts` (default http://127.0.0.1:8000).
# Set this when the UI must call the API directly (e.g. production build on a different host than the API).
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
